OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: Minister      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fapologises over            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F'inaccurate' veteran       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A government defence minister has      
OL,6, apologised after mistakenly saying a   
OL,7, British Afghan veteran took their own  
OL,8, life over the events in Afghanistan.   
OL,10,FJames Heappey first told Sky News he   
OL,11,Ffelt "sick to the bottom of my stomach"
OL,12,Fafter learning a soldier who served in 
OL,13,FAfghanistan had taken their own life.  
OL,15,FBut within minutes he told the BBC on  
OL,16,Fair the report may be inaccurate.      
OL,18,FThe Ministry of Defence said it was    
OL,19,Flooking into the report of the death - 
OL,20,Fbut it is understood to be untrue.     
